/reviews/tv-reviews/the-office-australian-remake-review-amazon-prime-video-3802616"><em>NME的</em>两星级评论</a>称其为“安全的重新构想，“由Déjàvu固定”。</p><p>最近，宣布将对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-office-is-getting-another-remake-this-time-in-mexico-3805792">Sit-Com进行墨西哥翻拍</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/oscar-nunez-is-going-to-be-in-the-office-spin-off-3842316">奥斯卡·努涅斯（OscarNuñez）将</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的“办公室”衍生产品。</p> ;
