detunji）。图片来源：Phil McCarten/CBS通过Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/jordan-adetunji-2000-x-1270-Phil-McCarten_CBS-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/jordan-adetunji-2000-x-1270-Phil-McCarten_CBS-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/jordan-adetunji-2000-x-1270-Phil-McCarten_CBS-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/jordan-adetunji-2000-x-1270-Phil-McCarten_CBS-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/jordan-adetunji-2000-x-1270-Phil-McCarten_CBS-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/jordan-adetunji-2000-x-1270-Phil-McCarten_CBS-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/jordan-adetunji-28-10-2024-3806799"><em>NME</em>封面</a>明星<a href="/artists/jordan-adetunji">Jordan Adetunji</a>在最近在伦敦售罄的头条展上带出了歌手<a href="/artists/kwn">KWN</a> 。查看下面的录像。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/jordan-adetunji-28-10-2024-3806799">Jordan Adetunji在封面上：“在2025年，我想直接接管”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p> Adetunji昨晚（2月27日）在首都的下部第三场比赛中演唱了他的最新歌曲和以前的歌曲，作为英国和他2025年世界巡回演唱会的一部分。这次巡回演出庆祝了爱尔兰明星的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jordan-adetunji-announces-new-mixtape-a-jaguars-dream-with-single-too-many-women-featuring-kwn-3828047">第二张混音带“捷豹的梦”，</a>而唱片中的单曲之一是以KWN为特色的“太多女性”。</p><p>当Adetunji首先说出“有吸引力”的“听起来很熟悉”的节拍分解之前，在演奏了“太多女性”之前的节拍分解。他开始演唱这首歌，对KWN的期待，电话上升了，他们最终在舞台上漫步地唱着她的诗歌使歌迷感到惊讶。</p><p>两人在最后一次合唱中进行了互动，然后吸引了人群“发出一些声音”。 </p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@iamasyax/video/7476252001089686806" data-video-id="7476252001089686806" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@IAMASYAX" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@iamasyax?refer=embed">@IAMASYAX</a></p><p>无法处理此@kwn @jordan adetunji <a title="Kwn" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/kwn?refer=embed">#kwn #kwn</a> <a title="Jordanadetunji" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/jordanadetunji?refer=embed">#jordanadetunji</a> <a title="Kehlani" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/kehlani?refer=embed">#kehlani</a> <a title="伦敦" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/london?refer=embed">#london</a> <a title="livemusic" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/livemusic?refer=embed">#livemusic</a> <a title="展示" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/show?refer=embed">#show #show</a> <a title="演出" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/gig?refer=embed">#gig</a> <a title="表现" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/performance?refer=embed">#performance</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬原始声音 -  asya💋💋" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7476252004248062722?refer=embed">♬原始声音 -  asya <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f48b.png" alt="💋" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f48b.png" alt="💋" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><p> Elsewhere in his set, the 26 year-old played &#39;YOU&amp;I&#39; – a throwback from his debut 2023 mixtape, &#39;Rock N Rave&#39; – and gave rock makeovers to &#39;Break The System&#39; and &#39;Options&#39; from &#39;A Jaguar&#39;s Dream&#39;, going back to his original roots as an indie rock star who was scouted by <a href="/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Me The Horizon</a> &#39;s <a href="/artists/oli-sykes">Oli Sykes</a> .</p><p>自从发布“ Rock n Rave”以来，他还对自己的职业生涯进行了反思：“这对我来说是一个重要的时刻，因为我正在制作很多音乐，当时没人真的很欣赏它。你们这里有些人很感激，我感谢你们。这就是为什么如果我对任何新艺术家有任何建议：这是一致性，伙计。一致性是关键。”</p><p> Adetunji将于本周日（3月2日）在La Boule Noire举行的2025年在巴黎举行的2025年巡回演出中完成英国和欧洲的比赛。然后，他将在美国的美国行动中进行一次简短的五场比赛，这将于3月15日在加利福尼亚大声的加利福尼亚结束。球迷们可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fjordan-adetunji-tickets%2Fartist%2F3268992" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到任何可用的门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFp8O4gpOKa/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60