#39;EP和KWN的病毒曲调“最差的行为”的混音。</p><p>邮<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jordan-adetunji-brings-out-kwn-at-sold-out-debut-london-show-3842297">报的乔丹·阿德图尼（Jordan Adetunji）在售罄的首张伦敦节目中带出KWN</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
麦当娜揭示了为什么她在情感上“不害怕死亡” https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-reveals-why-shes-not-afraid-afraid-of-death-in-sotional-note-note-note-3842313?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=madonna-reveals-why-shes-not-afraid-of-death-in-emotional-noteLiberty Dunworth Fri, 28 Feb 2025 12:53:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3842313 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="麦当娜在“庆祝之旅”中演出" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她用新帖子来反思母亲小时候的死亡</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-reveals-why-shes-not-afraid-of-death-in-emotional-note-3842313">麦当娜邮报揭示了为什么她“不惧怕死亡”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="麦当娜在“庆祝之旅”中演出" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/madonna@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/madonna">麦当娜（Madonna）</a>在社交媒体上分享了一封情感信，解释了她为什么“不怕死亡”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-pays-tribute-to-friend-who-saved-her-life-after-she-passed-out-on-bathroom-floor-and-woke-up-in-icu-3560359">麦当娜直播伦敦：流行女王与她的遗产斗争</a></strong></li></ul><p>流行偶像昨晚（2月27日）在她的Instagram帐户上分享了该帖子，反思了母亲小时候的死亡，并解释了损失如何导致她对死亡的看法改变。</p><p>她通过自己的<a href="https://www.instagram.com/stories/madonna/3577462060797712680/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">故事</a>发表了帖子，分享了她在11月写的一封信。</p><p> “我小时候，母亲去世了。在开放的棺材里看到她美丽的脸，亲吻她的红色嘴唇说再见，留下了令人难以忘怀的记忆。一个深厚的渴望。她对被遗弃的恐惧感到非常恐惧，”她开始说。</p><p> “我会跟随我的父亲到处都提醒他，如果他去世，我想和他一起埋葬。我对墓地着迷。”她补充说。 “我不怕死亡，因为我知道这是我再次与母亲在一起的唯一途径。</p><p> “随着生活的发展，我失去了许多我深爱的人，并将死亡视为永生的一种门。即使我的恋人离开我，我也将其视为一种死亡。当他们伤害我时，我会为他们葬礼。我会埋葬我对被遗弃的恐惧，然后才能超越我。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGlsmfISR76/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="