-e1476874999440-400x239.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/shrekforeverafter010710-1-e1476874999440-800x477.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1001px) 100vw, 1001px" /></p><p> <em>Shrek 5</em>的第一个预告片引起了在线粉丝的强烈反应，他们被新的角色设计所抛弃。</p><p>新的剪辑显示了菲奥娜和驴子的标题角色，他们在魔术镜中查看了受到在线模因的启发的史莱克的各种喜剧图像。</p><p>对图像做出反应，该小组与系列常规Pinocchio一起加入，并引入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zendaya">Zendaya</a>为史瑞克和菲奥娜的女儿。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">远处的最好的人来了。 <a href="https://t.co/7qn8FNIBT6">pic.twitter.com/7qn8fnibt6</a></p><p> - 史莱克（@shrek） <a href="https://twitter.com/Shrek/status/1895142370313666634?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年2月27日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>尽管剪辑的内容没有引起任何抱怨，但心爱的角色的新设计引起了争议。这是史莱克（Shrek）第一次，其余的演员自2010年以来一直在电影中<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-movie-11419-306799">永远上映</a>，</em>而艺术风格据说与最近的<em>《靴子续集》中最近的《猫》的</em>变化一致。</p><p>虽然技术和艺术技术可能在15年内发生了变化是可以理解的，但一些粉丝并不高兴。 “你们看到了……。他们对她做了什么？” X（以前是Twitter）上的一位用户说，更改之前和之后，菲奥娜（Fiona）并排。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">你们看到了吗……他们对她的<a href="https://t.co/XQtn4Xn1nT">pic.twitter.com/xqtn4xn1nt</a>做了什么</p><p>-  Tiktok Hater（@vancssasbeckett） <a href="https://twitter.com/vancssasbeckett/status/1895152921274372229?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年2月27日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>一位粉丝回想起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sonic-2-stars-reflect-on-original-design-controversy-they-were-right-3196106">过去的动画争议</a>，在那里，粉丝们对刺猬的最初设计不满意，并竞选了电影的延迟，角色的外观也发生了变化。</p><p> They said: “Can we bully dreamworks to change the <em>shrek 5</em> animation like we did to paramount to change <em>sonic</em> ’s animation?”, while another said “Shrek has had a style and look that hasn&#39;t changed since 2001. Now he&#39;s in the puss in boots art style, and it triggered everyone&#39;s fight or flight”.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> can we bully dreamworks to change the shrek 5 animation like we did to paramount to change sonic&#39;s animation? <a href="https://t.co/WkE82Czc8v">https://t.co/WkE82Czc8v</a></p><p> — chu (@THEHORRORGOTH) <a href="https://twitter.com/THEHORRORGOTH/status/1895147092173095023?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 27, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">史瑞克（Shrek）的风格和外观自2001年以来就没有改变。 <a href="https://t.co/U6hgKAuOvc">pic.twitter.com/U6hgKAuOvc</a></p><p> — (No) Signal (@NopeSignal) <a href="https://twitter.com/NopeSignal/status/1895149797524308280?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 27, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Further rejections included a tweet that said: “This is beyond losing the sauce. this is straight up disrespectful to the original art style”, while another asked: “Why does the animation look like an AI interpretation of what <em>Shrek 5</em> could look like”.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">这不仅是失去酱汁。 this is straight up disrespectful to the original art style <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f345.png" alt="🍅" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f345.png" alt="🍅" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f345.png" alt="🍅" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/Ga4OQ2bPtx">https://t.co/Ga4OQ2bPtx</a> <a href="https://t.co/3gzBIwD3o4">pic.twitter.com/3gzBIwD3o4</a></p><p> — Frankie Fey ✮ 