-Great-Circle2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Indiana-Jones-And-The-Great-Circle2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Indiana-Jones-And-The-Great-Circle2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Indiana-Jones-And-The-Great-Circle2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Indiana-Jones-And-The-Great-Circle2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> The <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation-5">PlayStation 5</a> version of <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/indiana-jones-and-the-great-circle">Indiana Jones And The Great Circle</a></em> could be released this April.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE:</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/indiana-jones-and-the-great-circle-review-game-pass-3827420">&#39;Indiana Jones And The Great Circle&#39; review: tip your fedora to this unexpected action delight</a></li></ul><p> <em>Indiana Jones And The Great Circle</em> launched for <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X/S</a> in December last year, and is also available on <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-game-pass">Xbox Game Pass</a> . The game was created by the Xbox-owned studio Bethesda but prior to launch, it was confirmed a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/indiana-jones-and-the-great-circle-confirms-release-date-and-playstation-launch-3785559">PlayStation version of <em>The Great Circle</em> was also in development.</a></p><p> At the time, it was announced that <em>Indiana Jones And The Great Circle</em> would be available for PlayStation gamers in Spring 2025 but now a new report from <em><a href="https://www.theverge.com/notepad-microsoft-newsletter/620839/microsoft-xbox-ai-gaming-muse-model-notepad" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Verge</a></em> claims developers are looking at an April release.</p><p> However, there are worries the launch could be delayed. “We&#39;re now waiting to hear if Indiana Jones is going to make Microsoft&#39;s target of an April release on PS5,” they wrote. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Official Launch Trailer: Indiana Jones and the Great Circle" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sq97d1RkdRM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <em>The Great Circle</em> was a surprise hit with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/indiana-jones-more-games-the-great-circle-success-3821192">LucasFilm saying they were now “super interested” in more <em>Indiana Jones</em> games</a> following its success. Developers are currently working on a DLC for <em>The Great Circle</em> called <em>The Order Of The Giants</em> , which will reportedly expand the early story of the main game and release at some point in 2025.</p><p> Set between the events of <em>Raiders Of The Lost Ark</em> and <em>The Last Crusade</em> , <em>The Great Circle</em> uses Harrison Ford&#39;s likeness but Indy was voiced by video game veteran Troy Baker for the project. “There&#39;s so much history going into this. There&#39;s so much expectation,” <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/indiana-jones-great-circle-voice-actor-troy-baker-3818632">he told <em>NME</em></a> . “I had to unburden myself from that pretty quickly. If I had stayed underneath the weight of that legacy, I&#39;d never have been able to do it.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/troy-bakers-indiana-jones-is-proof-hollywood-doesnt-need-ai-to-steal-actors-souls-says-harrison-ford-3835982">Praising Baker&#39;s performance</a> , Ford said: “You don&#39;t need artificial intelligence to steal my soul. You can already do it for nickels and dimes with good ideas and talent. [Baker] did a brilliant job, and it didn&#39;t take AI to do it.” It comes after <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/harrison-ford-praises-troy-bakers-indiana-jones-the-great-circle-3821894">the pair appeared onstage together at the 2024 Game Awards</a> . “I think this guy did a great job. If I&#39;d have known he was so good, I&#39;d have done it myself,” quipped Ford.</p><p> In other news, it&#39;s been revealed <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/this-is-why-the-wonder-woman-game-was-cancelled-3842275">why Warner Bros. Games scrapped</a> their <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/wonder-woman">Wonder Woman</a></em> game, despite spending a reported $100million on development.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/indiana-jones-and-the-great-circle-ps5-release-date-3842295">&#39;Indiana Jones And The Great Circle&#39; could be coming to PS5 this April</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
